name: Round cushion
description:
This beautiful cream and gold cushion will look lovely in any modern or country home setting.  To enhance the cushionâ€™s beauty, the edging is surrounded with gold, three-inch sheer single  ruffles with a gold and cream cross pattern on the facing. 

The  cushion measures  L16 inches  x  W16  inches and includes a zipper measuring nine inches. This cushion can also be used as cushion cover by unzipping the zipper and inserting your current cushion.

The cushion is made from rayon and cotton materials and as such,  I recommend dry-cleaning the cushion depending on the stain. To help maintain the beauty of the cushion, a quality upholstery protector was applied.

name: Bright maroon and gold cushion
description:
With a beautiful, light gold-green color on one side and bright maroon coloring on the other, this cushion will look lovely in any modern or country home setting.  To enhance the cushion beauty, there is a surrounding edging with a one-inch thick, decorative, and twisted piping integrated together to add both a touch of romance and modern look to your home. 

The  cushion measures  L17 inches x W17 inches and is zipperless.

The cushion is made from rayon and cotton materials and as such,  I recommend dry-cleaning the cushion depending on the stain. To help maintain the beauty of the cushion, a quality upholstery protector was applied.

name: Beautiful light green cushion
description:
This beautiful light green cushion   will look lovely in any modern or country home setting. The cushion cover measures L16 inches x W20 inches and includes six centered, medium-size pleats positioned left to right on the cushion cover facing and a zipper measuring sixteen inches. The cushion can be used as a cushion cover by unzipping the zipper and inserting your current cushion.

The cushion  is made from polyester and cotton materials and as such,  I recommend dry-cleaning the cushion depending on the stain.  To help maintain the beauty of the cushion, a quality upholstery protector was applied.
